    Generates the GNSS range errors due to signal in space, ionosphere and troposphere errors based on the elevation angles. This implementation is based on the equations defined in "Principles of GNSS, Inertial, and Multisensor Integrated Navigation Systems, Second Edition" and on the companion software available at: https://github.com/ymjdz/MATLAB-Codes/blob/master/Initialize_GNSS_biases.m
